611
00:27:33,009 --> 00:27:34,042
[Cell phone rings]

612
00:27:34,076 --> 00:27:35,777
Deb, hold on a sec.

613
00:27:35,811 --> 00:27:37,578
Hello?

614
00:27:37,613 --> 00:27:39,046
[Ominous music]

615
00:27:39,081 --> 00:27:40,648
I'll be right there.

616
00:27:40,682 --> 00:27:42,416
